      "text": [
        " اَلْمُحْرِمِ تَشَقَّقُ يَدَاهُ فَقَالَ «يَدْهُنُهُمَا بِزَيْتٍ أَوْ سَمْنٍ أَوْ إِهَالَةٍ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2658 - Muhammad ibn Muslim narrated from one of the Imams (as) regarding a Muhrim whose hands have cracked.\nImam (as) said: \"He may anoint them with oil, fat, or melted fat (ihalah).\""
        ]
      }
